title: Enchanted Journey.mp4
description:
Glicko the chipmunk lives in the city, but he wants to get to the Great Forest, where all chipmunks live; according to his friend the carrier pigeon Pippo.  He faces many dangerous enemies, and makes many new friends, along his journey.  Will he make it to the forest?
This is a classic Anime movie, that is very highly recommended and very enjoyable.

This film was made in 1984, and is a high quality MP4 file.
